Large Groups & Private Events
Looking for a unique and fun place to host a rehearsal dinner, wedding reception, bridal shower, wedding or a large party? 3 Keys Brewing can host your group in one of our 3 spaces. Details below!
Book an Event
We would love to host your next event! Are you having a team lunch or dinner, birthday party, retirement party, holiday party, family reunion, or any other type of get together? We have the space and experience to accommodate you and your guest!
We do offer a party menu for groups of 30 or more people on a single tab. Minimums may apply.
For all inquiries, please fill out the form below and we’ll be in touch soon.
Inquire Now
Cocktail Lounge
This quite room is perfect for private events. With direct access to the beer garden you and your guests can enjoy a private space while having the ability to enjoy beer garden activities.
Capacity:
50
Patio
Our large front patio can comfortably sit up to 75-85 people. Perfect for bridal showers, rehearsal dinners and other parties of 20+ people. Fully covered to keep the sun and rain away.
Capacity:
75
Dining Room
The inside dinning room is perfect for all types of events. We can comfortably sit up to 75 people.
Capacity:
75
Beer Garden
Designed specifically for large parties! The beer garden has a large covered stage, lots of tables with umbrellas and live music every Friday and Saturday!
Capacity:
250
